name: Purple Valley # Season 02
description:
Purple World is a utopia where’s no violence, nature is purple and your imagination is the only rule to be followed
 
Started as an AR experience, you can turn green items into purple ones in real time. 
People from all over the globe choose to use the ‘Purple Valley’ effect on a daily basis, with more than 150 million photos being taken since the filter’s release on over 60 countries
 
Now, with so much energy gathered around Earth, we can open the portal to Purple World. These cards are unique regions within that fantasy
